  "title": "ISic001090. I.Sicily inscription 001090",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρκεσὼι \n                    Αἰσχύλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρκεσὼι\">Ἀρκεσὼι</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αἰσχύλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Αἰσχύλου\">Αἰσχύλου</span></span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἥραι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἥραι\">Ἥραι</span></span>  <span data-text=\"εὐχάν\">εὐχάν</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρκεσὼι \n                    Αἰσχύλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρκεσὼι\">ΑΡΚΕΣΩΙ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αἰσχύλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Αἰσχύλου\">ΑΙΣΧΥΛΟΥ</span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἥραι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἥραι\">ΗΡΑΙ</span></span><span data-text=\"εὐχάν\">ΕΥΧΑΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001090_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 23-05-2022\" src=\"ISic001090_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001090.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 23-05-2022\" src=\"ISic001090-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text based on photograph</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Arkesoi, daughter of Aischylos, (fulfilled her) vow to Hera</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Ritschl 1866 138 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001643\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001643</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">271</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Manni Piraino 1973 55 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531</a></li><li> Dubois 1989 <a href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">56</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Deeply incised letters without serifs. Broken bar alpha; eipsilon with shorter middle bar; small omicron above the line; Sigma somewhat open; smaller and open omega with short horizontal tails.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.5.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.5</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Λ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Λ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Χ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Χ type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ω-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ω type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ω-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ω type1.1</a> </p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
